Küpper, M., Müller-Ebert, D., Ebert, M., Scheuvens, D., Schladitz, A., Schütz, L., & Weinbruch, S. (2011). 
Electron microscopy of particles collected at Praia, Cape Verde, during the Saharan Mineral Dust Experiment: 
Particle chemistry, shape, mixing state and complex refractive index. Tellus B, 63(4), 475–496. 
https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1600-0889.2011.00550.x

[2d] For use of the Panta algorithm, please cite: Panta, A., Kandler, K., Alastuey, A., González-Flórez, C., 
González-Romero, A., Klose, M., Querol, X., Reche, C., Yus-Díez, J., & Pérez García-Pando, C. (2023). Insights 
into the single-particle composition, size, mixing state, and aspect ratio of freshly emitted mineral dust from 
